，诱导用户重新安装。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.v2ex.co/03x8g8iZ.png\"/></p>\n<p>都 21 年了，没有相关部门管管吗</p>\n","last_modified":1635298231,"replies":14,"id":810838},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_large.png?m=1629391403","name":"create","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_normal.png?m=1629391403","title":"分享创造","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","topics":16846,"footer":"","header":"欢迎你在这里发布自己的最新作品！","title_alternative":"Create","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1629391403","stars":4081,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":17,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"username":"hzcer","website":"","github":"","psn":"","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a00b/a776/30135_mini.png?m=1512209567","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hzcer","tagline":"","twitter":"","created":1354277984,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a00b/a776/30135_mini.png?m=1512209567","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a00b/a776/30135_mini.png?m=1512209567","location":"","btc":"","id":30135},"last_reply_by":"v2ka","last_touched":1635299572,"title":"找出非 Mac App Store 的应用并替换它","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/810817","created":1635295961,"deleted":0,"content":"写了个找出所有非 MAS 的应用，然后查找是否存在对应的 MAS 版本。\r\n\r\n## 为什么这么做：\r\n* 使用 MAS 的更新机制而不是应用自己的，可以不打开应用自动更新，也可以不用一些例如 Microsoft AutoUpdate 的更新应用。\r\n* MAS 上架有审核有 sandbox ，防止应用作恶\r\n* 安装卸载更加简单无残留？\r\n\r\n---------\r\n\r\n项目地址: https://github.com/rwv/AppStorify <br/>\r\nMac App Store 下载: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/appstorify/id1591245624 <br/>\r\n\r\nP.S 除了 swift 写的 GUI ，还有 Python 写的 CLI 版本。\r\n\r\n## 截图\r\n\r\n![screenshot]( https://github.com/rwv/AppStorify/blob/main/img/README/Screenshot.png?raw=true)","content_rendered":"<p>写了个找出所有非 MAS 的应用，然后查找是否存在对应的 MAS 版本。</p>\n<h2>为什么这么做：</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>使用 MAS 的更新机制而不是应用自己的，可以不打开应用自动更新，也可以不用一些例如 Microsoft AutoUpdate 的更新应用。</li>\n<li>MAS 上架有审核有 sandbox ，防止应用作恶</li>\n<li>安装卸载更加简单无残留？</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<p>项目地址: <a href=\"https://github.com/rwv/AppStorify\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/rwv/AppStorify</a> <br/>\nMac App Store 下载: <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/appstorify/id1591245624\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://apps.apple.com/us/app/appstorify/id1591245624</a> <br/></p>\n<p>P.S 除了 swift 写的 GUI ，还有 Python 写的 CLI 版本。</p>\n<h2>截图</h2>\n<p><img alt=\"screenshot\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://github.com/rwv/AppStorify/blob/main/img/README/Screenshot.png?raw=true\"/></p>\n","last_modified":1635296161,"replies":14,"id":810817},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_large.png?m=1630643933","name":"mbp","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_normal.png?m=1630643933","title":"MacBook Pro","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/mbp","topics":7347,"footer":"","header":"State-of-the-art processors. All-new graphics. Breakthrough high-speed I/O. Three very big leaps forward.","title_alternative":"MacBook Pro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_mini.png?m=1630643933","stars":2967,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":10,"parent_node_name":"apple"},"member":{"username":"tysb777","website":null,"github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0344b43a67721463995cc1163609a89b?s=24&d=retro","bio":null,"url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/tysb777","tagline":null,"twitter":null,"created":1545880265,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0344b43a67721463995cc1163609a89b?s=24&d=retro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0344b43a67721463995cc1163609a89b?s=24&d=retro","location":null,"btc":null,"id":373258},"last_reply_by":"mcluyu","last_touched":1635306398,"title":"MacBook Pro 14/16 可以自己拓展加存储内存?","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/810905","created":1635305451,"deleted":0,"content":"根据网友晒出的 MacBook Pro 14/16 拆截图，Apple 预留了硬盘的位置，是否可以后期自己加装硬